# Copy to `.env.neon` at repo root and fill values (file is gitignored).
# Created from Neon MCP: `list_projects`, `get_connection_string`, `provision_neon_auth`.
#
# Loaded automatically by `@afenda/env-loader` for:
#   - `apps/api` (dev + start)
#   - `packages/_database` Drizzle CLI (`db:migrate`, etc.)
#   - `apps/web` Vite config (so `vite.config.ts` sees the same env as the API)
#
# --- Neon project (non-secret identifiers) ---
# NEON_PROJECT_ID=
# NEON_BRANCH_ID=
# NEON_DATABASE=neondb
#
# --- Postgres (secret: password in URI — rotate in Neon Console if leaked) ---
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOSTPOOLER/neondb?sslmode=require
#
# --- Neon Auth (public HTTPS endpoints; optional if browser uses Neon Auth) ---
# NEON_AUTH_BASE_URL=https://<endpoint>.neonauth.<region>.aws.neon.tech/<database>/auth
# NEON_AUTH_JWKS_URL=https://<endpoint>.neonauth.<region>.aws.neon.tech/<database>/auth/.well-known/jwks.json
#
# --- Better Auth (self-hosted in `apps/api` — use with DATABASE_URL above) ---
# BETTER_AUTH_SECRET=   # openssl rand -base64 32  OR  MCP-generated
# BETTER_AUTH_URL=http://localhost:5173
# DEMO_TENANT_ID=       # optional UUID; must exist in `tenants` after migrations
#
# --- API process ---
# PORT=3001
